text: Alfredo Sone (born 17 September 1965) is a Chilean equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Chilean male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Chile Category:Equestrians at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
